{"tid":1742822,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"721 元朗襲擊四個月　至今僅控 6 人　元朗站下午 2 時關閉","createTime":"2019-11-21T02:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T08:57:01.000Z","uid":201669,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7a945cc54a5a03cc569d017b4247d7dbce5a5ddc","tid":1742822,"uid":201669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:56:08.000Z","msg":"721元朗襲擊四個月，根據政府資料，至今有 36 人被捕，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>惟僅有 6 人被正式控告參與暴動及串謀有意圖而傷人等罪</strong></span></span>，案件現由警方新界北總區重案組第二隊調查。<br />\n另外港鐵深夜公布，因應與相關政府部門進行的風險評估，元朗站將今日（11月21）於下午2時關閉，列車不停元朗站。<br />\n包括「飛天南」、燒烤場東主等6人早前各被控一項參與暴動罪，早前於粉嶺裁判法院再提堂，6人被加控串謀而有意圖傷人罪名，指控他們串謀惡意傷害他人。6人暫毋須答辯，案件押後至12月4日再訊，將轉介區域法院。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n守護言論與新聞自由。立場新聞，寸步不退。<br />\n每月贊助支持立場新聞"},{"pid":"d737f057a8184a053e0c585488681e7631b2904d","tid":1742822,"uid":201669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:57:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33faeeeb8b4f8283d397b7a5d09eff82dec184ba","tid":1742822,"uid":31528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:58:00.000Z","msg":"是日精選笑話: 香港仲有法治"},{"pid":"19d81a59e31b7b0ef92d1250727dc12b12495b5d","tid":1742822,"uid":201669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:58:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d0aa06f241bde7d7d8cd67f74f70d4e69ef813a","tid":1742822,"uid":201669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e8c126ebdb4f633115df2a5687bf1c2f286f05","tid":1742822,"uid":258598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:09:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b899fd8659009ee3513b56a8b0aaaa190cb6f5b","tid":1742822,"uid":201669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:15:0